title: Nadodimannan
subTitle: Padmanabhan, a man who joins political rallies to make money, gets into trouble when he is elected mayor of Thiruvananthapuram and is forced to fight corruption in the city.

title: Mersal
subTitle: Maaran, a doctor, is falsely arrested for the murder of his colleague, Dr Arjun Zachariah. He soon discovers that the real culprit is a lookalike who aims to expose corruption in the medical industry.

title: Leela
subTitle: Notorious for his relationships with women, a single Kuttiyappan's life takes a turn when he sets out to fulfil one of his strange dreams.

title: Captain
subTitle: Kannayiram, a powerful gangster, kills Ramasamy, for not giving up his land to him. After hearing this news, Shiva, Ramasamy's brother, flees the military camp to avenge his brother's death.

title: Premam
subTitle: Vikram falls in love with different women at various stages of his life and with each experience, he bears the pain and emotions of separation.

title: Srungaravelan
subTitle: Kanan falls in love with Raddhu, the daughter of a ruthless city gangster responsible for numerous deaths. To marry her, Kanan must confront the dangers and challenges that lie ahead.

title: Purusha Pretham
subTitle: While SI Sebastian is known for his brilliant stature, his claims are put to the test after he misplaces a body. Trouble and chaos ensue when a woman alleges the dead man to be her husband.

title: Nerariyan CBI
subTitle: Years after a young woman, Mythili, is murdered in a supposedly haunted mansion, Sethurama Iyer, a CBI officer, decides to find the culprit and solve the mystery.

title: Android Kunjappan Version 5.25
subTitle: After Subramanian has to leave his aged father alone to go to russia, he returns with a robot to take care of him. Even though hesitant at first, his father soon develops a strong bond with the robot.

title: Chinthamani Kolacase
subTitle: Lal Krishna, an eccentric criminal lawyer, defends the woman accused of Chinthamani's murder. However, he learns that there is more to the story and decides to dispense justice in his own way.

title: Chinthamani Kolacase
subTitle: Lal Krishna, an eccentric criminal lawyer, defends the woman accused of Chinthamani's murder. However, he learns that there is more to the story and decides to dispense justice in his own way.

title: Oru Black and White Kudumbam
subTitle: Antony, a lorry driver, struggles with an inferiority complex stemming from his skin colour, leading him to create ongoing problems for his family.

title: C U Soon
subTitle: Jimmy gets ensnared in a web of uncertainty when his fiancee goes missing, leaving a suicide note. Later, Kevin assumes the mantle to unravel the enigma.

title: Mulla
subTitle: Lachi, whose father died mysteriously, falls in love with Mulla. Later, Mulla adopts an abandoned baby while Bharathan, who killed Lachi's father and the baby's parents, tries to separate them.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Kunjiramayanam
subTitle: Kunjiraman's plan to marry Thankamani fails when his cousin, Laalu, breaks their union. Later, Kunjiraman goes to Gulf to make money and returns to take revenge on Laalu.

title: Avatharam
subTitle: Kuppaswamy, an innocent theatre enthusiast, falls in love with visually challenged Ponnama after joining a troupe. When the troupe struggles financially, the couple moves to the city.

title: Pushpa 2: The Rule
subTitle: A powerful smuggler goes head-to-head with a vengeful enemy while controlling politics and managing high-stakes confrontations. A public apology sparks a tense showdown, culminating in a challenge.

title: Chettayees
subTitle: Friends John, Kichu, Roopesh, Bava and Babumon decide to have a party on New Year's Eve. However, a series of events leads to a lot of unpleasantness and a rift between John and Kichu.

title: Drishyam 2
subTitle: Georgekutty, a cinema hall owner, is a changed man who thrives in life. However, when his family become entangled in a criminal investigation, he must protect them from the legal institution.

title: Chunkzz
subTitle: The lives of four friends Romario, Riyas, Yoodas and Athmaram, take a dramatic turn when a girl joins their mechanical engineering class.

title: Chunkzz
subTitle: The lives of four friends Romario, Riyas, Yoodas and Athmaram, take a dramatic turn when a girl joins their mechanical engineering class.

title: Colours
subTitle: Dr. Rajalakshmi enjoys life with her two daughters, Pinki and Pooja. However, when she uncovers a major pharmaceutical fraud, she becomes the target of dangerous enemies determined to silence her.

title: Parava
subTitle: Irshad and Haseeb, two teenage boys from Mattanchery, share a passion for pigeon flying, a local game. Later, Irshad opens up about a tragic incident that ruined many friendships in the neighbourhood.

title: Greetings
subTitle: Gopan falls in love with his neighbour, Sheethal. After learning that Sheetal has a plan to reunite a separated couple, he also pools in ideas, which leads to many unexpected events.

title: Chandrolsavam
subTitle: Sreehari has returned home from Paris after six years. He tries to settle some scores and clear misunderstandings with his old friends before leaving his village.

title: Puthan Panam
subTitle: Nityananda Shenoy, a gangster from Kasaragod, decides to exact revenge on an ex-minister who swindled him right before demonetisation. Meanwhile, Muthuvel and his mother struggle to survive in Kochi.

title: Keshu Ee Veedinte Nadhan
subTitle: The life of an ordinary driver Keshu turns upside down when he wins a lottery worth 12 crores but his morality gets tested.

title: Naran
subTitle: Velayudhan, an orphan, is loved by the villagers as he keeps the village free from unsavoury people and practices. However, an evil moneylender and politician get jealous and try to get rid of him.

title: Thuruppugulan
subTitle: Menon buys land for his five-star hotel and asks his trusted employee, Sreedharan Unnithan, to take its charge. Years later, Unnithan gets Menon imprisoned in a fake case and Kunjumon helps him.

title: Janatha Garage
subTitle: When Anand visits Hyderabad, he encounters Sathyam, who operates an organisation aiding the underprivileged. Sathyam, swayed by Anand's vision, hands over the organisation's management to him.
